    <h3>How to speed up access Facebook?</h3><br>
    You can do following things:
    </td>    
    </tr>
    
    <tr>
    <td>    
    1, Access "Friends", this enable you cache your friends data, when you access news feed, no need get your friends data one by one.<br>
    2, Access "Phonebook" this enable you cache your Phonebook, if you want the latest data, just press option menu "Refresh".<br>
    </td>    
    </tr>
    </table>   
    <br>
    <table>
    <tr>
    <td>
    <h3>How to synchronize your Phonebook with Address book?</h3><br>    
    </td>    
    </tr>
    
    <tr>
    <td>    
    1, Turn on "Synchronize address book" in setting. If already turned on, Facebook application will do sync in background automatically.<br>
    2, Open Contact application, select "Sync with Facebook", and make sure your have turned on "Synchronize address book".<br>
    </td>    
    </tr>
